parameters:
\nw[Taro]Hmmm, so this is the place... Alright, let's
proceed with caution.
\nw[Nonna]Now we can listen to Shia's song.

\nw[Taro]Ah, so verifying the curse means singing... When I
heard it at the Water Temple, I had to restrain my
voice, so I'm looking forward to it.

\nw[Huma]Since The Songstress of Azure is known for its
intense songs, I've never heard things like
lullabies before~
\nw[Kuno]Well then, let's go with Shia again.

\nw[Kuno]Did it show on your face? I'm sorry, Taro, even
though you're working too.

\nw[Kuno]It seems like I'm jealous of Shia. But I also want
to be like Shia, so you don't have to worry about
it.
\nw[Taro]Is that so? Well, if you say so...

\nw[Taro]Well then, let's return to the surface. When we
need to hurry back, we can use the \C[2]Return
Stone\C[0] to come back quickly.
